Phase 5 — Distribution Switchover (One Domain)
Risk: Medium — consumer-facing change. Managed via view swap.
What you do:
The consumer-facing surface for this domain is currently a pivot MV. The switchover is implemented as a view rename or synonym swap — not a consumer SQL change.
