RDM DI reports for this domain are retired
EAV tables for this domain become read-only (retained for historical queries, archived on schedule)
What changes: Distribution queries UDM arb table for this domain. Option A EAV pipeline stops.
What stays the same: Consumer SQL unchanged. All other domains unchanged.
Value delivered:
First domain fully on UDM — real production value
EAV pipeline cost eliminated for this domain
Full attribute-level DI in production
Precedent and confidence for subsequent domains
Phase 6 — Organic Domain-by-Domain Migration
Risk: Decreasing with each domain — engine is proven, process is established.
Repeat Phases 4 and 5 for each remaining domain. Each domain is independent. The engine is generic — adding a domain is catalog entries, not code changes.
